Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Independents switch to Reagan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w4v1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Oct 1980
Campaign sees Carter's support slipping as independent voters switch to Reagan. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.